beer.beer_description:
The spicy chemistry between the throuple of rum, ginger, and lime is one of the cocktail world's unparalleled trios. Built on the unwieldy foundation of a 13.7% rum-barrel aged imperial stout, this Dark & Stormy inspired beer is both bright and tropical while simultaneously broody and mysterious.

Try not to get lost.
